  "text": "It must be pointed out that each modality does offer additional information(e.g. pitch, prosody in speech signal) beyond merely its presence or absence at a given moment. While such information can certainly be utilized to improve the recognition performance [CITATION_1] [18], utilizing such additional information is not the focus of this work. However, our framework does not preclude such a possibility.",
